mology in Tom McCarthy\u2019s C\u201d. C21 Literature: journal of 21st-century writings, 5(3) 2017, p.&nbsp;3. DOI: http://doi.org/10.16995/c21.26\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:McCarthy, Tom}}\n[[Category:21st-century English novelists]]\n[[Category:1969 births]]\n[[Category:People educated at Dulwich College]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Writers from London]]\n[[Category:Alumni of New College, Oxford]]\n[[Category:Believer Book Award winners]]\n[[Category:English male novelists]]\n[[Category:21st-century British male writers]]\n[[Category:The New Yorker people]]\n", "name_user": "Sadads", "label": "safe", "comment": "linkdebut novelusingFind link", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_McCarthy_(novelist)"}
